= hRecipe Type 0.2.1 =
* Renamed plugin to 'hRecipe Type' and updated other meta info.
* Added custom post type for recipes.
* Added custom taxonomy for recipes.
* Added custom meta boxes to recipes.
* Custom formatting for to comply with the hRecipe microformat.
* Added default template for the recipe custom post type.


